data.description: Lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home with City water & sewer in an established SW Cape Coral neighborhood. NEW ROOF 2023 freshly painted exterior! This home offers a screened front entry & a welcoming floor plan with a spacious living & dining area, vaulted ceilings, tile flooring throughout the living area & laminate flooring in the bedrooms. The kitchen has plenty of counter space & a large breakfast bar. The dining area has sliders to the screened lanai where you can enjoy your morning coffee overlooking the lush landscaping in the fully fenced backyard with plenty of room for your dream pool. The split bedroom floor plan allows privacy for the master suite with features a walk-in closet & en suite bathroom with dual sinks.  This would be the perfect starter home, investment or rental
